# Supabase Table Naming Convention

## Golden Rule
Before creating or querying ANY table: **read `docs/LEO_DB_SCHEMA.schema` first**.
After creating ANY table: **update `docs/LEO_DB_SCHEMA.schema` immediately**.

## Naming
- Every table: `myday_<name>` — NEVER `leo_`, `user_`, or unprefixed
- Verify name against schema file before writing SQL or `.from()` calls

```sql
-- ✅ GOOD
create table if not exists myday_fitness_data ( ... );

-- ❌ BAD (violated 2026-03-31, caught by user)
create table if not exists leo_fitness_data ( ... );
create table if not exists user_google_tokens ( ... );
```
